<h1>What happened when the Guardian editor met Piers Morgan</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline"><!--proximic_content_on-->As the Editor of 'The Guardian', Alan Rusbridger presides over an institution that prides itself on occupying the ethical high ground. But how would he stand up to scrutiny when 'GQ' magazine sent Piers Morgan along to grill him?<!--proximic_content_off--></p>
	<!--
    Create a list of all articles, collections and links which are "from the archives"
-->
<!--
    Create a list of all articles, collections and links which are "from the archives"
-->
